    "en": {
      "title": "Ready to help Sri Lankan people: Indian President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian President Thirulapathi Murmu has said that India is ready to help the people of Sri Lanka.",
        "The Indian High Commission in Sri Lanka has posted a congratulatory message on its official Twitter page.",
        "At the same time, Indian President Tirolpati Murmu also said that the long-term bilateral partnership will be further strengthened based on deep people-to-people relations. (a)"
